00:10:03,433 --> 00:10:05,087
- No.
- No.

167
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:09,585
Ma se abbocca qualcosa, so cucinarteli
al vapore in foglie di banano.

168
00:10:10,888 --> 00:10:15,172
